{"name": "nonebot-plugin-sendmsg-by-bots", "metadata": {"name": "nonebot-plugin-sendmsg-by-bots", "version": "0.1.6", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["nonebot-adapter-onebot", "nonebot2"], "summary": "a send msg tools", "upload_time": 1719152902}, "documentation": ["<div align=\"center\">x\n  <a href=\"https://v2.nonebot.dev/store\"><img src=\"https://github.com/A-kirami/nonebot-plugin-template/blob/resources/nbp_logo.png\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" alt=\"NoneBotPluginLogo\"></a>\n  <br>\n  <p><img src=\"https://github.com/A-kirami/nonebot-plugin-template/blob/resources/NoneBotPlugin.svg\" width=\"240\" alt=\"NoneBotPluginText\"></p>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n# nonebot-plugin-sendmsg-by-bots\n\n_\u2728 NoneBot \u591abot\u53d1\u9001\u6d88\u606f \u2728_\n\n\n<a href=\"./LICENSE\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/nek0us/nonebot-plugin-sendmsg-by-bots.svg\" alt=\"license\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/nonebot-plugin-sendmsg-by-bots\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/nonebot-plugin-sendmsg-by-bots.svg\" alt=\"pypi\">\n</a>\n<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.10+-blue.svg\" alt=\"python\">\n\n</div>\n\n## \ud83d\udcd6 \u4ecb\u7ecd\n\n\u8ba9\u8fde\u63a5\u7684\u6bcf\u4e2abot\u53d1\u9001\u6d88\u606f\uff0c\u5982\u65e0\u597d\u53cb\u6216\u7fa4\u5219\u8df3\u8fc7\n\n## \ud83d\udcbf \u5b89\u88c5\n\n<details open>\n<summary>\u4f7f\u7528 pip \u5b89\u88c5</summary>\n\n    pip install nonebot-plugin-sendmsg-by-bots\n</details>\n<details open>\n<summary>\u4f7f\u7528 conda \u5b89\u88c5</summary>\n\n    conda install nonebot-plugin-sendmsg-by-bots\n</details>\n\n\n\n## \ud83c\udf89 \u4f7f\u7528\n### \u6307\u4ee4\u8868\n\n```bash\nfrom nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots import tools\n# \u53d1\u9001\u7fa4\u6d88\u606f\uff08\u80fd\u53d1\u90fd\u53d1\uff09\uff1a\nawait tools.send_group_msg_by_bots(group_id: int,node_msg: Message|MessageSegment|str)\n# \u53d1\u9001\u7fa4\u6d88\u606f\uff08\u53ea\u53d1\u6210\u529f\u4e00\u6b21\uff09(self_id \u53ef\u9009\uff0c\u9009\u4e86\u4e4b\u540e\u6307\u5b9a\u54ea\u4e2aid\u7684bot\u8d26\u53f7\u53d1\u9001\uff09\uff1a\nawait tools.send_group_msg_by_bots_once(group_id: int,node_msg: Message|MessageSegment|str,self_id: Optional[str] = None)\n# \u53d1\u9001\u7fa4\u5408\u5e76\u6d88\u606f\uff08\u80fd\u53d1\u90fd\u53d1\uff09\uff1a\nawait tools.send_group_forward_msg_by_bots(group_id: int,node_msg: list)\n# \u53d1\u9001\u7fa4\u5408\u5e76\u6d88\u606f\uff08\u4e00\u6b21\u6536\u624b\uff09\uff1a\nawait tools.send_group_forward_msg_by_bots_once(group_id: int,node_msg: list,self_id: Optional[str] = None)\n# \u53d1\u9001\u79c1\u804a\u6d88\u606f\uff08\u80fd\u53d1\u90fd\u53d1\uff09\uff1a\nawait tools.send_private_msg_by_bots(user_id: int,msg: Message|MessageSegment|str)\n# \u53d1\u9001\u79c1\u804a\u6d88\u606f\uff08\u53ea\u53d1\u6210\u529f\u4e00\u6b21\u6536\u624b\uff09\uff1a\nawait tools.send_private_msg_by_bots_once(user_id: int,msg: Message|MessageSegment|str,self_id: Optional[str] = None)\n# \u53d1\u9001\u79c1\u804a\u5408\u5e76\u6d88\u606f\uff08\u80fd\u53d1\u90fd\u53d1\uff09\uff1a\nawait tools.send_private_forward_msg_by_bots(user_id: int,msg: list)\n# \u53d1\u9001\u79c1\u804a\u5408\u5e76\u6d88\u606f\uff08\u4e00\u6b21\u6536\u624b\uff09\uff1a\nawait tools.send_private_forward_msg_by_bots_once(user_id: int,msg: lis,self_id: Optional[str] = Nonet)\n# \u88ab\u52a8\u56de\u590d\u6d88\u606f\uff0c\u4ee5\u62c9\u683c\u5170md\u5f62\u5f0f\u53d1\u9001\nawait tools.send_text2md(text: str):\n\n# group_id : \u7fa4\u53f7\n# user_id : \u597d\u53cbqq\u53f7\n# node_msg : \u5408\u5e76\u8f6c\u53d1\u6d88\u606f\u5217\u8868\n# msg : \u6d88\u606f\n\n# \u53d1\u9001\u6210\u529f\u4f1a\u8fd4\u56deTrue\uff0c\u5426\u5219\u4f1a\u8fd4\u56deFalse\n\n# \u4ece\u6240\u6709bot\u7684\u7fa4\u5217\u8868\u68c0\u7d22\u7fa4\u4fe1\u606f\n# \u672a\u68c0\u7d22\u5230\u4f1a\u8fd4\u56de {\"group_name\":\"\u672a\u83b7\u53d6\u5230\u7fa4\u540d\",\"group_id\":group_id}\ngroup_info = await tools.get_all_group_info(group_id:int)\n# \u4ece\u6240\u6709bot\u7684\u7fa4\u5217\u8868\u68c0\u7d22\u7fa4\u6210\u5458\u5217\u8868\nmember_list = await get_group_member_list(group_id: int)\n\n```\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.__plugin_meta__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.__version__", "xref": {"fqname": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.config.__version__", "project": null}}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.Config", "xref": {"fqname": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.config.Config", "project": null}}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.PluginMetadata", "xref": {"fqname": "nonebot.plugin.PluginMetadata", "project": "nonebot2"}}]}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.config", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.config.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.config.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.config.Config", "bases": ["BaseModel"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.config.Config.plugin_enabled", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.tools", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "nonebot_plugin_sendmsg_by_bots.tools.send_forward_msg", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "bot", "type": {"name": "Bot", "xref": {"fqname": "nonebot.adapters.onebot.v11.bot.Bot", "project": "nonebot-adapter-onebot"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "id", "type": {"name": "int", "xref